Here is a CSV file containing the information you requested for the first five presidents of the United States:

| Name | Age when Started Office | Year Started Office | Number of Years Served |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| George Washington | 57 | 1789 | 4 |
| John Adams | 62 | 1797 | 2 |
| Thomas Jefferson | 60 | 1801 | 4 |
| James Madison | 53 | 1809 | 4 |
| James Monroe | 59 | 1817 | 4 |

Note: The ages listed are the ages at which each president started their term, not the ages they were when they were elected.
